This is a top notch business sim game. Cute art, just enough things to fiddle with without getting overwhelming, and good progression. The simulated races are fun and add excitement to the game that you don't see in Kairosoft's biggest hit Game Dev Story. Also, it's nice that it has landscape view support.  UI is a bit clumsy; it's obvious that it was ported from mouse & keyboard controls, and functions like swiping simply don't exist. Furthermore, the UI is inconsistent, sometimes using scroll bars for long lists and other times making you browse pages left to right.   Still the underlying game is very fun, if a little on the easy side. Highly recommended and definitely worth the price.
